Package: RightCIBERSORTxTools
Title: Reference Matrix And Mixture File Builder For CIBERSORTx
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alexis", family = "Varin", email = "alexis.varin@inserm.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-3474-7263"))
Description: This package provides a set of tools to generate CIBERSORTx input files from RNA-seq data,
    namely a Reference Matrix (a Seurat object's RNA counts in a tab delimited txt file with cell identity as column name)
    and a Mixture File (a tab delimited txt file with each column containing CPM of a bulk RNA-seq or microarray experiment)
    all in a single function.
